        public MFGroundOverlayOptions mapUrl(@NonNull

        Set map url for ground overlay. The map url must be in the correct format. For example with the url https://example.com/1/2/3.png 1 = zoom level 2 = x 3 = y The map url sample: https://example.com/{z}/{x}/{y}.png
